     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="9"/>
   <lg>
      <l>Candide des veniam, placidū nec contra<gap reason="illegible" resp="#oxf" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>e frontem,</l>
      <l>Inficiat chartas, si qua litura meas:</l>
      <l>Nec mihi sollucem, nec praebuit aura calorē</l>
      <l>Me tenebris cinctum frigida zona premit:</l>
      <l>Sin redeat mihi fausta dies, si deni{que} Phoebus</l>
      <l>Lumine, percutiat lumina nostra, suo:</l>
      <l>Tum nitar meliora sequi, tū menda vicissim</l>
      <l>Tot mihi lux a biget, quot mihi lux aperit.</l>
   </lg>
